node.text:
My double patties burger was decent, not outstanding and the whole buying process was pleasant. Reasonably priced, the pickles and sauce were good but fries arrived soggy (which was expected).
.
I might do a return purchase, only to determine if this was a fluke or how things really are given they’re new. Even so I wouldn’t go all out to convince anyone they absolutely need to try it.
.
Limited to 30 buns daily, visit tinyurl.com/thedirtybuns to place your orders. Islandwide delivery is available at flat-fee of $4 per location. 10% off for self pick up at 102 Henderson Road S159562, Sprouts Hub. For full menu, visit @dirtybunsg
